expressing goodwill.

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:16.719
This way,

00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:19.360
King Liang poses little threat now.

00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:32.319
Everything is normal on Sister's end?

00:02:34.039 --> 00:02:34.560
Yes.

00:02:35.080 --> 00:02:37.199
I occasionally go
to organize her incense.

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:39.599
The Grand Princess still prays
day and night.

00:02:40.159 --> 00:02:40.840
Furthermore,

00:02:42.080 --> 00:02:43.280
she has lit an eternal lamp.

00:02:48.879 --> 00:02:50.280
She still refuses to see me.

00:02:51.639 --> 00:02:52.759
Everyone in the palace knows

00:02:52.919 --> 00:02:54.360
you cherish the Grand Princess most.

00:02:55.199 --> 00:02:56.120
For over a year now,

00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:58.599
you've scoured for treasures
to send to Weiyang Palace.

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:00.680
Maybe

00:03:01.350 --> 00:03:03.000
