I covet this throne?

00:05:41.600 --> 00:05:43.519
I once stood atop power's pinnacle,

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:45.680
surveying all below.

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:49.720
I've also been trampled underfoot,

00:05:50.800 --> 00:05:51.959
brought near death's edge.

00:05:56.480 --> 00:05:58.040
